{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Noschehlojeet winnu wiſſi/ tas apfahrt winnu irr/ un wiſſi/ kas winna Wahrdn paſſist/ fakfajt: Ka irr ta ſtipra Rihſte / un tas glihts Sisls Inhsis?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nolaideeß no tawas Goh-Dihas/ dſihwo iſkalſufchäs Weetâs/ tu Eedsihwotaja/ tu Meita no Dibona/ jo Moaba Pohſtitajs irr prett tewim zehlees/ un tawus Stiprunus ſamaittajis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Stahwi Zelt-Mallâ/ un uherangi tu Eedsihwotaja no Aroëra/ waiza to (Wihrn/) kas behg/ un to iſbehguschu See-wu/ fakfi: Kas irr notizzis?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Moabs irr Kauna tap-pie/ jo tas irr iſbeedinachts/ knu-zeet un fleedſeet / paſludddinajeet eeffch Arnena/ ka Moabs irr iſpohſtihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta Sohdiba irr nahkuſi pahr to klatju Seimini/ pahr O-lonu/ un pahr Jaſzu/ un pahr Merwaotu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pahr Dibonu/ un pahr Nebu/ un pahr Bet-Dib-lataimu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pahr Kiriataimu/ un pahr Bet Gamulu/un pahr Bet Meonu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pahr Kiriotu/ un pahr Bazru/ un pahr wiſſeem Pilſ-fahteem tahs Moaba Semmes/ kas tahfu un tuwu irraid.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Moaba Rags irr no-zirſts/ un winna Elſons irr fa-trechts/ fakka tas KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Peedsirdinajeet winau jo wiꞥſch irr prett to KUNGU pa-augſtinajes/ ta ſchnauge Moabs Rohkas fawa Ween-ſchanâ/ un buhs ir pats pa Apfineekli.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo neggt Ifraëts irr teim par Apfineekli bijis? bija wiꞥſch tad ſtarp Sagteem atrafs: Tu tad/ tapehz ka tu prett winnu effi runnajs/ tapſi pats ats-wefts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Atſtabjeet tohs Pilſfab-tus/ un dſihwojeet Afimina-Ralndß/ juhs Eedsihwotaji no Moaba/ un tohpeet ka Ballo-dis/ kas iſdohbejſchôs Plaitu-môß Ligſdu darra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Mehs eſſam Moaba Lep-nibn dſirdejſchi/ ka tas tohti lepus irraid/ ir winna Augſumu/ un winna Lepnibu/ un winna Greſ-nibu/ un winna Sirõs Pa-augſtinachnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet es paſihſtu winna Dutunu/ bet tas ne iſdohfees/ fakka tas KUNGS: un winna Leelischana to ne padarrihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tadeht kaufschn es pahr Moabu/ un pahr wiſſu Moabu gribbu es kleegt/ un pahr teem Laudim no Kireres waidecht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "(Itt ka) pahr Jaëseru/ ta gribbu es pahr tewi raudaht/ tu Wihta-Rohks no Sibinas/ ta was Wihta-Stibgas irr pahr Juhen zehluschees/ un irr peeſneeguschees liths Jaësera Jub-rai/ tas Pohſtitajs irr pahr ta-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
